snippet.title: Wedding Peach (SNES) Longplay [433]
snippet.description: So I don't know what this is, or what it's from, but all I know is the green haired girl is a damn cheater. The art style is cool at least but the mini games are trash, I get the last laugh at the end of the game though. Oh and yeah and obviously this was a blind longplay and i'll never play it again.
